=== Phrases: simple
--- kwim
<bold content>
--- html
<p><strong>content</strong></p>

=== Phrases: empty argument
--- kwim
<bold::content>
--- html
<p><strong>content</strong></p>

=== Phrases: simple with single argument
--- kwim
<bold:important:content>
--- html
<p><strong class="important">content</strong></p>

=== Phrases: simple with multiple arguments
--- kwim
<bold:quite important:content>
--- html
<p><strong class="quite important">content</strong></p>

=== Phrases: key-value argument
--- kwim
<bold:id="item32":content>
--- html
<p><strong id="item32">content</strong></p>

=== Phrases: key-value argument
--- kwim
<bold:id="item32":content>
--- html
<p><strong id="item32">content</strong></p>

=== Phrases: key-value argument; escaped colon
--- kwim
<bold:id="item3\:2":content>
--- html
<p><strong id="item3:2">content</strong></p>

=== Phrases: argument plus leading space
--- kwim
<bold:quite important: content>
--- html
<p><strong class="quite important"> content</strong></p>

=== Phrases: argument plus trailing space
--- kwim
<bold:quite important:content >
--- html
<p><strong class="quite important">content </strong></p>
# XXX - I think the space should be preserved here
# <p><strong class="quite important">content</strong></p>

=== Phrases: leading colon
--- LAST
--- kwim
<bold :leading>
--- html
<p><strong>:leading</strong></p>


