=== Phrases: lots of colons in content
--- kwim
<bold :colons:everywhere:>
--- html
<p><strong>:colons:everywhere:</strong></p>

=== Phrases: lots of colons in content; empty arg
--- kwim
<bold:::colons:everywhere:>
--- html
<p><strong>:colons:everywhere:</strong></p>

=== Phrases: args and colons in content
--- kwim
<bold:important::colons:everywhere:>
--- html
<p><strong class="important">:colons:everywhere:</strong></p>

=== Phrases: no content
--- kwim
<bold>
--- html
<p><strong/></p>

=== Phrases: args but no content
--- kwim
<bold:important:>
--- html
<p><strong class="important"/></p>

=== Phrases: arg but no content, no trailing colon
--- kwim
<bold:important>
--- html
<p><strong class="important"/></p>

=== Phrases: args but no content, no trailing colon, spaces in args
--- kwim
<bold: quite important >
--- html
<p><strong class="quite important"/></p>

=== Phrases: no name
--- kwim
<:important:content>
--- html
<p><span class="important">content</span></p>

=== Phrases: nested
--- kwim
<bold <emph bold italic>>
--- html
<p><strong><em>bold italic</em></strong></p>

=== Phrases: nested with class
--- kwim
<bold <emph:variable: bold italic>>
--- html
<p><strong><em class="variable">bold italic</em></strong></p>

=== Phrases: nested with angles in values
--- kwim
<bold:data-info="<oops>":<emph bold italic>>
--- html
<p><strong data-info="&lt;oops&gt;"><em>bold italic</em></strong></p>


